<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <%- include('../partials/head')%>
    <title>Tourmy | <%= specificProduct.name %></title>
</head>

<body>
    <main class="container-fluid container-show">
        <%- include('../partials/navbar')%>
        <div class="breadcrumb"><a href=/<%=category%>><%=category.charAt(0).toUpperCase()+category.slice(1)%> </a>
                <span>|</span> <span><%= specificProduct.name %> </span></div>
        <div class="show-image">
            <img src="<%=specificProduct.image%>" alt="">
        </div>

        <div class="show-info">
            <h1><%= specificProduct.name %></h1>
            <h4>$<%= specificProduct.price %>.00</h4>
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit, amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Aliquam, unde voluptates fugit harum
                dignissimos id sapiente repellendus dolores hic neque, quas accusamus, cupiditate libero qui odit ut
                atque dolore quisquam. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Officiis natus nemo
                culpa tempore modi temporibus perferendis quibusdam exercitationem error ratione tenetur asperiores
                aspernatur, quia nesciunt ullam libero odit amet quisquam?</p>

            <div class="show-btn">
                <button>Add To Cart</button> <button>Customize</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="image-carousel">
            <a target="_blank" href="<%=specificProduct.image%>">
                <img src="<%=specificProduct.image%>" alt="" class="image-thumbnail">
            </a>

            <a target="_blank" href="<%=specificProduct.image%>">
                <img src="<%=specificProduct.image%>" alt="" class="image-thumbnail">
            </a>

            <a target="_blank" href="<%=specificProduct.image%>">
                <img src="<%=specificProduct.image%>" alt="" class="image-thumbnail">
            </a>

        </div>

        <div class="video embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9">
            <iframe class="embed-responsive-item" src="<%= specificProduct.video %>" allowfullscreen></iframe>
        </div>

        <div class="recommend">
            <h1 class="header">You May Also Like</h1>
            <div class="recommended-boards">
                <% for(let i = 0; i < 4; i++) {%>
                <div id="surfboard<%=i+1%>" class="featured-boards-panel">
                    <a href="/surfboards/<%=featuredSurfboards[i]._id %>">
                        <img class="product-img" src="<%=featuredSurfboards[i].image%> " alt="">
                        <h2 class="product-name"><%= featuredSurfboards[i].name %></h2>
                        <h6 class="product-price">from $<%=featuredSurfboards[i].price%>.00</h6>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <%  }%>
            </div>
        </div>
        <%- include('../partials/footer')%>
    </main>
    <%- include('../partials/bootstrap_cdn')%>
</body>

</html>